(65595, 13730, 0, 1, 'No Regret (acoustic 側錄)', '這是一首蓄勁能量的歌，要再出發的感覺\n希望各位在低潮的時候不要放棄\n堅持下去，就會有屬於你的舞台。', '2013-07-14 00:00:00', 2013, 1, 1, 1, '', '主歌：\n\nit''s been a long time since\nthat i''ve lost my mind\n\nbut i''ve found my self in the\nblink of your eyes\n\nnow i have to change myself\nto against the rights\n\nyou''d better watch out cause\nI am coming by\n\n\n\nlit up my cigarette the\nsmokes rounds my face\n\nwalk down the streets to look\nfor a place to stay\n\nnow I am sitting right in\nfront of a cafe''\n\nready to face the things that\ni''ve got to face\n\n\n\npre chorus：\n\nthis time i want to fix every\nmistakes\n\nthis time i want to be free\nagain\n\nnow i know i have to begin\nwith my guys and my faith\n\n\n\n副歌：\n\ni''ve try so hard to stand on\nthe place i''ve ever want\n\nto show you that i want to\nexpress my heart\n\nno i won''t step back i''ll\nstand still on my ground\n\nto fight for my faith i''ll be\nno regret', 262, '', 'Oscar', '黃保', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-07-14 01:29:32', '2015-03-12 14:01:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(65596, 141235, 5618, 12, '凡人', '', '2013-07-23 00:00:00', 2013, 20, 0, 4, '這個世界有千百種人生\n你的人生有沒有可能如我所想\n\n有時候，我會覺得\n是不是太看好你了，其實你就是凡人一個\n\n你拿著我的信用在半空中甩盪\n你總等著自己的錯誤無聲的發酵啊\n\n人生不過就是如此，嬉鬧啊\n交織出故事吧', '', 238, '', '邱比', '邱比', 'Chiu-Pi', 'Chiu-Pi / Gallery', '', 1, 0, 1, '2013-07-14 03:38:16', '2013-12-25 00:34:09', '2013-12-25 00:34:09'),
